## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/incoming">Incoming</a> for lane maks phi as machine instruction, incoming register <code>Reg</code> and incoming block <code>Block</code> are taken from machine instruction.

<code>UpdatedReg</code> (if valid) is <code>Reg</code> lane mask merged with another lane mask.
